    // DESCRIPTION
    section
        div(class="container whoami mt-0")
            div(class="whoami__description")
                strong Problem Solving 
                | and 
                strong concentration 
                | are my best skills. My goal is to learn and the work environment is the best place where I can 
                strong study
                | . I find it a stimulating place, where I can get involved and try to solve IT problems and more.
    // MY SKILLS
    section
        div(class="container skills")
            h3(class="skills__title section-title") My Skills
            div(class="swiper")
                div(class="swiper-wrapper", style="height: 64px")
                    div(class="swiper-slide")
                        img(src="/images/c.png", alt="C Language Logo")
                    div(class="swiper-slide")
                        img(src="/images/cpp.png", alt="C++ Language Logo")
                    div(class="swiper-slide")
                        img(src="/images/c-sharp.png", alt="C# Language Logo")
                    div(class="swiper-slide")
                        img(src="/images/java.png", alt="Java Language Logo")
                    div(class="swiper-slide")
                        img(src="/images/python.png", alt="Python Language Logo")
                    div(class="swiper-slide")
                        img(src="/images/php.png", alt="PHP Language Logo")
                    div(class="swiper-slide")
                        img(src="/images/mysql.png", alt="MySql Logo")
                    div(class="swiper-slide")
                        img(src="/images/typescript.png", alt="TypeScript Language Logo")
                    div(class="swiper-slide")
                        img(src="/images/js.png", alt="JavaScript Language Logo")
                    div(class="swiper-slide")
                        img(src="/images/html.png", alt="HTML Language Logo")
                    div(class="swiper-slide")
                        img(src="/images/css.png", alt="CSS Language Logo")
                    div(class="swiper-slide")
                        img(src="/images/sass.png", alt="SASS Language Logo")
                    div(class="swiper-slide")
                        img(src="/images/react.png", alt="React Library Logo")
                    div(class="swiper-slide")
                        img(src="/images/docker.png", alt="Docker Logo")
                    div(class="swiper-slide")
                        img(src="/images/debian.png", alt="Debian Logo")
                    div(class="swiper-slide")
                        img(src="/images/ubuntu.png", alt="Ubuntu Logo")
                    div(class="swiper-slide")
                        img(src="/images/github.png", alt="GitHub Logo")
    // MY PROJECTS
    section
        div(class="container projects")
            h3(class="projects__title section-title show-hidden") My Projects
            div(class="hidden-content")
                div(class="project")
                    h3(class="project__title")
                        | That
                        div(style="flex-grow: 1")
                        a(target="_blank", href="https://github.com/J-Dany/Chat")
                            img(src="/images/github.png", alt="Link to That! on Github")
                    p 
                        | An open source chat made up of 3 components: Chat, Chat Client and Chat WS. Every component has its own aim.
                    p 
                        strong Chat 
                        | is the real server, handling messages and client connections.
                    p
                        strong Chat Client 
                        | is the web app that users will use.
                    p
                        strong Chat WS 
                        | is the component responsible for registering users and get the chat history between two users.
    // MY PASSIONS
    section 
        div(class="container passions")
            h3(class="passions__title section-title show-hidden") My Passions
            div(class="hidden-content")
                div(class="passion")
                    h3(class="passion__title") Linux
                    p 
                        | In my free time I like to study to improve the use of the Linux operating system. I have experience in 2 very famous linux distributions: <strong>Debian</strong> and <strong>Ubuntu</strong>. 
                        | In addition, I also have experience with <i>Raspbian</i>. Right now I'm studying to pass the LPI texts. Being a very adopted system in servers, I think it will do much to improve my skills as a system administrator.

    // MODAL CONTACT ME
    div(class="modal fade", id="modalContactMe", tabindex="-1", data-bs-backdrop="static", aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel", aria-hidden="true")
        div(class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered")
            div(class="modal-content")
                div(class="modal-header")
                    h5(class="modal-title") Leave me a message!
                    button(type="button", class="btn-close", data-bs-dismiss="modal", aria-label="Close")
                div(class="modal-body")
                    form(name="formContact", action="", method="GET", enctype="text/plain")
                        input(type="hidden", name="subject", value="Email from Portfolio Website!")
                        div(class="form-group mb-3")
                            label(class="form-label", for="from") From
                            input(class="form-control", placeholder="Who are you?", id="from", name="from")
                        div(class="form-group mb-3")
                            label(class="form-label", for="contact") Contact
                            input(class="form-control", placeholder="Email or telephone number", id="contact", name="contact")
                        div(class="form-group mb-3")
                            label(class="form-label", for="request") Request
                            input(class="form-control", id="request", placeholder="Request title", name="request")
                        div(class="form-group mb-3")
                            label(class="form-label", for="body") Message
                            textarea(class="form-control", id="body", name="body", rows="3", placeholder="Request message")
                    div(class="d-none p-3 bg-success text-white", id="successMessage") Thanks! I will contact you as soon as possible!
                div(class="modal-footer")
                    button(class="btn btn-secondary", data-bs-dismiss="modal") Close
                    button(class="btn btn-primary", id="submitFormContact") Submit
  
